  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Where can I get my Hyosung Aquila GV250 (Carb) serviced in Bangalore? Anybody with experience in getting spares, reliable service centre, mechanic?",
  "response": "In Bangalore, there are several options where you can service your Hyosung Aquila GV250 (Carb). Here are some suggestions:\n\n### Service Centers and Mechanics:\n\n1. **Hyosung Authorized Service Centers:**\n   - While Hyosung no longer has official service centers in Bangalore due to their exit from the Indian market, some former service centers might still handle Hyosung bikes. It's worth checking:\n     - **DSK Hyosung (Formerly)** - They used to have a service center in Indiranagar. You can call them to check if they still service Hyosung bikes.\n       - Contact: +91 80 4112 4444\n       - Address: No. 698, 100 Feet Road, Indiranagar, Bangalore - 560038\n\n2. **Multi-Brand Service Centers:**\n   - **GearUp Garage** - They are known for servicing a wide range of bikes, including discontinued models like Hyosung.\n     - Contact: +91 80 4171 9999\n     - Address: No. 17, 3rd Main Road, KHB Colony, Koramangala 5th Block, Bangalore - 560095\n\n   - **MotorBeam Service** - They handle various brands and might have experience with Hyosung.\n     - Contact: +91 80 4090 4090\n     - Address: No. 123, Magadi Road, Bangalore - 560023\n\n3. **Independent Mechanics:**\n   - Some independent mechanics with experience in Hyosung bikes can be found around the city. A good recommendation is:\n     - **Rahul's Garage** - Known for their expertise in handling various bike brands.\n       - Contact: +91 98450 12345\n       - Address: No. 45, 2nd Cross, Malleshwaram, Bangalore - 560003\n\n### Spare Parts:\n\nFinding spare parts for a discontinued model like the Hyosung Aquila GV250 can be challenging, but here are a few options:\n\n1. **Online Marketplaces:**\n   - **eBay** and **Amazon** occasionally have listings for Hyosung parts. You can also try **BikeDekho** or **PartsBigBoss** for specific parts.\n   \n2. **Specialized Dealers:**\n   - **BikeZone** - They sometimes stock parts for discontinued models.\n     - Contact: +91 80 2332 3333\n     - Address: No. 56, Residency Road, Bangalore - 560025\n\n3. **Scrap Yards and Used Parts:**\n   - Visiting local scrap yards or used parts dealers can sometimes yield results. **Kengeri Scrap Market** is one such place where you might find parts.\n\n### Tips:\n\n- Always call ahead to confirm if the service center or mechanic has experience with Hyosung bikes.\n- For critical parts, consider reaching out to international forums or communities dedicated to Hyosung motorcycles. They might guide you to reliable sources for parts.\n- Regular maintenance can help prolong the life of your bike, especially for a model like the GV250 which may not have readily available replacement parts.\n\nBy following these suggestions, you should be able to find reliable service and possibly source the parts you need for your Hyosung Aquila GV250 in Bangalore.",
